How to configure rules in wazuh: 
rules creation 
example : use case : password sprying detection 
number of attempts : 



to create a custum rule we need to : 
  create a custum decoder to extract the fields we need and their values.
  create the corresponding custom rule to generate the alert according to our requirements 

/var/ossec/etc/decoders : to stock custum decoders 
/var/ossec/etc/rules : to stock custum rules 
/var/ossec/ruleset : default rules folder : overwritten when we upgrade the wazuh-manager installation
